  "texts": [
    "The fine-tuning fails with the M4F4, where we observe a significant increase in model perplexity.",
    "This is primarily attributed to a single quantization constant used for a larger count of weights.",
    "Each ReRAM crossbar is of the size 128*128, with a 2-bit representation per cell.",
    "When a 4-bit representation is utilized in M4F4, approximately 8,000 numerical values are quantized using a single constant.",
    "This results in suboptimal representation where certain bins are underutilized or completely unused."
  ],
